cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper deals with natural language processing techniques to summarize information during crises. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper deals with crisis response, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
